OpenCV Test project "Convert color image to gray image"

---------------------------------
OS: manjaro linux(arch)

Install OpenCV
    sudo pacman -Syu
    sudo pacman -S opencv

Verify installation
    pkg-config --modversion opencv4

----------------------------------
g++ -std=c++17 main.cpp -o opencv_demo -I/usr/include/opencv4 -lopencv_core -lopencv_imgproc -lopencv_imgcodecs

./opencv_demo input.jpg output.jpg

output.jpg â†’ grayscale image
